Great Depression Day simulator.

MAKE SURE TO READ MANUAL/DISCRIPTION BEFORE PLAYING!

Last night, you climbed into bed. You had just had a normal day in 2019. Your dreams contained time travel for some reason. You don't know why. You have just woken up in a strange place. You are not in your bed and you are not in your room. This place looks really old fashioned. "I must be dreaming you thought to yourself" but when you tried to wake up, you couldn't. You realized that you must be in a different time.

Explore the world around you and try not to go insane, if you do, the game ends. Have fun!

