You are in the a Street.
You can see a Mob of People.
You can go in or north.
> look at mob of people

> look at mob of people
They are really poor, they live on the streets because they can't afford to live in a house. These sights do have an effect on you but not that much, since you are a snob.
They contain a Rock Soup.

> look at rock soup

> look at rock soup
This seems to be something that these people ate. It must be so gross and flavorless. You see people taking rocks and putting them in their pots and boiling them. They must do this for minerals. You think of all the nice things that you eat every day and how you take them for granted. You feel sympathetic for these people.
> speak to mob of people

> speak to mob of people
HELP US!!! Please, we are all staving and dying, please kind soul, help us! PLEASE!!!
You start to think that maybe you were wrong. That these people do really matter. You start to feel more humble.
> give money mob of people

> give money mob of people
They thanked you for giving them $15 but they begged you for more. You felt somewhat good about what you had done, but the thought of them starving and dying, would cling to you forever.
